      "   Method: Propensity Score Matching + Inverse Probability Weighting\n",
      "âœ“ Causal bias detector ready\n",
      "\n",
      "ğŸ”¬ Confounders Prepared:\n",
      "   â€¢ Event severity (keyword count)\n",
      "   â€¢ Geographic region (coastal vs inland)\n",
